{
  "stem": "26983.12",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was-- and there was no food anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the people who were a bit stronger, they grabbed it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes you got few crumbs, but it was hopeless.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then, I think it was Friday night on the 4th or 5th of May, we heard the SS left the camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were looking around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everyone was running to the place where they distributed the food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everyone tried to grab something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember I grabbed some cube of marge, and I put it in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Margarine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Margarine and maybe a few pieces of sugar, and-- and a piece of bread, also.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they came-- stronger, Russian or other prisoners-- and I tried to keep my pockets that they shouldn't take it away.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But again, I was saved in two ways.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I would eat the marge, I would die because we couldn't eat any fat things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If-- they saved me that they stole it from me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And how they stole it-- we were very clever, and didn't let him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he took a kind of razor and cut the pocket and took it out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, we knew the war is over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a tremendous [INAUDIBLE] and screaming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we decided, next morning, a friend of mine--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not yet.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the next morning, we decided we will go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, we had two options.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Most of the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of the friends went back from the little towns they came from-- Lambach, Wels, and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was on the way from where we came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we decided we will go a different direction.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And again, in a way, this saved us.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
